+### TRemix - Telegram Messenger for Android
+
+TRemix is a messaging app using the foundation of Telegram's focus on security and speed, with quality of life tweaks. The goal is to maintain feature and update parity with the primary application but with user annoyances solved, and more pro features implemented.
+
+As we implement our changes, we will slowly develop TRemix's identity to make it unique.
+
+***
